I might be able to explain the missing mic. Over time some of the analog parts of it would break...causing a buzzing in the audio line coming from the mic circuit...a quick fix is to take out the mic so you don't get the annoying mic noise mixed in.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3369">Jeroen</a> — Fri Apr 27, 2012 4:07 pm</p><hr />
